                  <div id="flush-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">A: Notes is a web application that allows users to create, edit, and delete notes from their personal dashboard.</div>
